Introduction

K-TIGERS ZERO (Korean: 케이타이거즈제로; Japanese: ケイタイガーゼゼロ) is a 12-member co-ed group under K-Tigers E&C. They officially debuted on September 19, 2019 with the mini album '희로애락' with the tracks ‘Now’ and ‘Side Kick’.
